<epp:page xmlns:epp="http://eprints.org/ep3/pages" xmlns:epc="http://eprints.org/ep3/control" title="Repository Policies">
  <h1>Repository Policies</h1>

  <h2>Content Description</h2>
  <p>This is a metadata catalogue for ARCOM CM Abstracts. It provides metadata for discovery and linking purposes only. No full-text content is available via this interface.</p>

  <h2>Metadata Policy</h2>
  <p>The metadata provided through this interface may be used for non-commercial purposes, provided that proper attribution is given to the source. Commercial use of the metadata requires prior written permission.</p>

  <h2>Data Policy</h2>
  <p>This catalogue does not provide access to full-text content via the OAI-PMH interface. For access to full-text content, please contact the relevant rights holders directly.</p>

  <h2>Submission Policy</h2>
  <p>This is a metadata catalogue, not a full repository. Submissions are restricted to metadata only.</p>

  <h2>Contact Information</h2>
  <p>For further information, please contact the Abstracts Manager at <a href="mailto:{$c->{adminemail}}">{$c->{adminemail}}</a>.</p>
</epp:page>

